BACKGROUND.name = "Lunatic"
BACKGROUND.description = "You are stark raving madâ€¦ or that is what the others believe. You have no concept of what the future holds or what had occurred in the past. Your actions are confused at best or incomprehensible at worst. The way in which you deal with matters is erratic and chaotic with no sense of direction or coordination. Anyone seeing you act for a meer moment would consider how you have lasted this long. Your disillusions are kept to yourself and the reasons for it are certainly only known by the God Emperor for only he would have the willpower to understand your lunacy. No one knows why you are here and some people prefer to keep away from you due to fear or disinterest. Only the Emperor knows how long you will last here."
